title: Easy Astral Projection Method / 4 A.M. Wake Back To Sleep
description:

***This video shows you how to transfer consciousness into the etheric body which is located in the 4D plane using the "WAKE BACK TO SLEEP" process.

***Here's the steps listed below:

1) Start the Mantra in the morning. 
2) Eat your last meal around 5-6pm.
3) Go the Sleep around 10pm.
4) Set Alarm for 4am.
5) Wake up for 30 minutes. 
6) Write the Mantra.
6) Go back to bed at 430am.
7) Start breathing exercise. 
8) Start *PROTECTION SHIELDING.
9) Activation of Chakra Centers. 
10) Sensing the 4D Etheric legs/ arms.
11) Do the Roll Out of Body technique. 
12) With your 4D Body move over 10 feet away from the physical body. 
13) Free to explore consciousness inside your 4D Etheric body.  This is the closest energy body to our physical bodies so we're focusing on the easiest body to astrally project too.
